<p>Hold Still focuses on three themes - helpers and heroes, your new normal and acts of kindness - with the final 100 tackling subjects including family life in lockdown, the work of healthcare staff and the Black Lives Matter movement.</p>

<p>One entry shows a woman during an anti-racism protest holding a banner which reads, 'Be on the right side of history' while another sees Captain Sir Tom Moore give a thumbs up to the camera.</p>

